en_4173954_0	COLOMBO (News 1 st )- The police sources say that former Sri Lankan Ambassador to Russia Udayanga Weeratunga is currently in Dubai.
en_4173954_1	Sources confirmed that discussions were held recently with the United Arab Emirates on steps that could be taken to bring him back to Sri Lanka.
en_4173954_2	According to the reports UAE has informed Sri Lanka, that they would make necessary arrangements on the matter according to their laws.
en_4173954_3	The CID has appointed a special team to carry out investigations on Udayanga Weeratunga.
en_4173954_4	Udayanga Weeratunga who is on the run has been named as a wanted fugitive and is being hunted by Sri Lankan authorities, the United Arab Emirates as well as the Interpol.
